          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-39-1705061441452-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender and the chicken is cooked through, remove the dish from the oven and add your <strong>blanched peas</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven, covered, for a final 3 min or until the peas are warmed through – this is your<strong> oven-baked Durban chicken curry</strong></p><p>Discard the bay leaf[ves] from the curry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
